{
  "_comment": "Human-readable mirror of catalog.FullEstateInput(\"digitalocean\", \"Frankfurt\", ...). The authoritative source is internal/catalog/full_estate.go; this JSON is documentation only. pd-MIG-PLAN-DRYRUN-ESTATE.",
